    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding? there's nothing to rebuild. the person who did that work is gone. the version of me that believed in those theories died when they were debunked. it's not just a mistake, it's like the whole foundation of my life was a hallucination. i'm just staring at a blank space where a person used to be.",
